Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
Hi, where can I find the reports in the platform for analyzing. Like breakdown by age, gender, countries and etc?

Hey there! You can find detailed reports on your ad performance in the reporting section of NewsBreak’s Ad Manager. This section allows you to run custom reports and audience insights, where you can analyze data by age, gender, and other demographics. You can also filter data by campaigns or ad sets and select a specific date range for analysis. For more details, check out this guide: [Reporting Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18088532505485-Reporting-Guide).
